data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!   2 HOMES FOR THE PRICE OF ONE!!! NO HOA AND NO RENTAL RESTRICTIONS!!!Welcome to your dream ranch property!  This stunning multi- family three-bedroom, two-bath home sits on a spacious .9 acre lot and offers more than meets the eye. This property also includes an additional separate building  with one bedroom, one bathroom set up for an in-law suite or apartment to rent!     Step inside the main house where you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan.  The living area features ample natural light, enhancing the beauty of the interior.   The kitchen is a chef's delight with modern appliances, plenty of counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. The master suite is a true retreat, boasting a private bath and generous closet space.  Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of room for family or guests.  You'll appreciate the convenience of a second full bathroom.    But that's not all!!!  This property also includes a fantastic apartment or in-law suite, complete with a bedroom, full bath, and a screened-in-porch- perfect for enjoying peaceful evenings.  Additionally, there's an oversized room that can serve as a home office, studio, workshop, or entertainment space.    Outdoors, you'll find a 12X20 fully functional barn with electricity, offering endless possibilities for storage or creative projects.  And for those interested in sustainable living, an added bonus is the chicken/hen coop complete with friendly chickens that provide fresh eggs daily.  Imagine farm-fresh eggs right from your own backyard!    The expansive .9 acre lot offers plenty of space for gardening, outdoor activities or even future expansion of a pool.  With this property, you'll have the space an amenities to live the life you've always dreamed of.  Don't miss out on this rare opportunity- schedule your visit today and make this beautiful ranch property your new home!
